  m_Name: Kids
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  npcName: Alty
  _npcRating: 0
  _isFinalNode: 0
  _lines:
  - Ah, well I've known Jersey since he was young.
  - He was different then.
  - He held a lot of pain in his heart...
  - So much rage.
  - I've tried to lend him a hand...
  - But even now he refuses.
  - He insists on "walking his own path"
  - I suppose everyone has to grow up eventually.
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - What about you?
  - It's important to be independent.
